<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.5">
<l>paṭavara vucci taṉmēl pāyntupaṉ ṉaṭaṅkaḷ ceytu</l>
<l>maṭavaral maṅkai taṉṉai mārvakat tirutti ṉāṉē</l>
<l>taṭavarai taṅku māṭat takupukaḻ nāṅkai mēya</l>
<l>kaṭavuḷē kāva ḷantaṇ pāṭiyāy kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having performed many dances, leaping on the top of the hooded serpent,</l>
<l>[You] who sat a naive lady on [your] chest,</l>
<l>You of the cool hamlet of Kāvaḷam, god who dwells in praiseworthy Nāṅkai</l>
<l>With mansions built [like] wide mountains, only you are [our] refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
